revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yeldells}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yeldell'' is the 32339<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 712 individuals. ''Yeldell'' is most common among Black/African American (71.77%) and White (23.88%) individuals.
